Question #1 - Explain the rhetorical strategy used in the first two paragraphs: repetition of animal imagery.

Animal Umagery - Relevent to cultural beliefs
  The wrestler is caled a cat and Okonkwo is called a fish.
        Okonkwo is the underdog (Fish) which is taking on the more dominant person (Cat) who defies the odds, which were agianst him. 
        
